{"type": "article", "id": 3748, "title": "可以涂鸦的饼干", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-21T08:09:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052332461tEghS8sTknNrW05.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t圣诞季马上就要到了，来自纽约的高档美食超市 Dean &amp; DeLuca 日前推出了一款童心满满的产品「Color Me! Thanksgiving Cookies」。从产品名称即可看出，这是一款可以随意涂鸦的饼干，设计师将这套饼干套装里的饼干造型精心地设计为圣诞树、火鸡等造型，表面的蛋白糖霜犹如一张展开的画布，拿着套装配带的五色彩笔就可以在饼干上尽情涂鸦。值得注意的是，Dean &amp; DeLuca 为套装特意选择了可食用的墨水，所以即使是涂鸦过的饼干也可以放心食用。定价 39 美元，<a href=\"http://www.deandeluca.com/color-me-thanksgiving-cookies.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233245qMKWPSbd9I6JDQeY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233245iKw9NzeWSXjyFDIM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233245CjhK1TeEuXmvHFdr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}